general_description.prompt_text: Describe what you see in this image. Include the setting, main elements, colors, lighting, and overall composition. Be specific and detailed. Form the response as a continuous paragraph. Maximum 200 words.
general_description.response: The image showcases a modern kitchen with a warm and inviting ambiance, characterized by its light beige walls and a ceiling with recessed lighting that casts a soft glow throughout the space. The kitchen features rich, dark wood cabinetry with a glossy finish that contrasts beautifully with the lighter tones of the walls and floor. The flooring is a light wood laminate, adding to the room's natural and cozy feel. A prominent feature is the central island, which has a curved countertop and is supported by white columns, creating a focal point in the room. Above the island hangs a unique, circular chandelier with multiple arms, each holding a pot or pan, adding a functional and decorative element. The island also houses a built-in sink and a set of black bar stools with wooden seats, inviting a casual dining or social area. To the right, a stainless steel refrigerator stands tall, complementing the modern aesthetic. The overall composition is balanced and harmonious, with a mix of natural and industrial elements that create a stylish and functional kitchen space.

foreground_background.prompt_text: Describe the foreground elements (closest to viewer) and background elements (distant/setting) separately. Explain what appears in each layer and how they relate to each other. Form the response as a continuous paragraph. Maximum 200 words.
foreground_background.response: In the foreground of the image, the viewer's attention is drawn to a set of four black metal bar stools with wooden seats, neatly arranged around a curved, light-colored wooden bar counter. Above the bar, a circular metal rack with hooks holds an assortment of pots and pans, adding a functional and decorative element to the space. The background, slightly out of focus, reveals a spacious kitchen area with dark wood cabinetry and a stainless steel refrigerator, which contrasts with the lighter tones of the bar and the floor. The ceiling is composed of white square tiles, and a large skylight allows natural light to illuminate the entire room, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. The floor, partially visible, features a light wood finish with a darker border, which complements the overall color scheme of the kitchen while adding a subtle visual interest. The relationship between the foreground and background elements is one of depth and function; the bar and stools serve as a focal point, inviting the viewer to imagine sitting and enjoying a drink or meal, while the background provides the context of a well-equipped and stylish kitchen.

entities_interactions.prompt_text: Identify all people, animals, and objects in the image. Describe what they are doing and how they interact with each other. Focus on actions, relationships, and connections between elements. Form the response as a continuous paragraph. Maximum 200 words.
entities_interactions.response: The image depicts a modern kitchen with a central island that serves as a focal point. The kitchen is devoid of people and animals, focusing instead on the objects and their arrangement. The central island, with its curved counter and white columns, acts as a bar area, complete with three black metal bar stools. Above the island hangs a unique chandelier with multiple chains and hooks, from which several pots and pans are suspended, adding a functional yet stylish touch. The kitchen cabinets, finished in a rich brown wood, line the walls, providing ample storage. A stainless steel refrigerator stands to the right, complementing the modern aesthetic. The floor features a light wood finish with a dark border, adding contrast and sophistication to the space. The overall design suggests a well-thought-out layout, emphasizing functionality and style, with each element carefully chosen to create a cohesive and inviting kitchen environment.

mood_emotions.prompt_text: Describe the mood and emotions conveyed by this image. What feelings does it evoke? Consider whether the overall tone is positive, negative, or neutral. Explain what visual elements contribute to this emotional atmosphere. Form the response as a continuous paragraph. Maximum 200 words.
mood_emotions.response: The image evokes a sense of warmth and comfort, primarily due to the inviting and well-organized kitchen space. The neutral color palette, with its beige walls and wooden cabinets, creates a calm and serene atmosphere, suggesting a peaceful and relaxing environment. The natural light streaming in through the large window enhances the feeling of openness and tranquility. The stainless steel appliances, including the refrigerator and oven, add a modern touch, while the hanging pot rack above the island introduces a touch of functionality and style, making the space feel both practical and stylish. The wooden island with its dark brown finish and the matching bar stools provide a cozy spot for casual dining or conversation, further contributing to the welcoming and homely mood. The overall tone of the image is decidedly positive, as it presents a harmonious blend of functionality and aesthetics, inviting viewers to imagine themselves in a comfortable and well-designed kitchen.

structured_inventory.prompt_text:
Analyze this image and create a JSON object documenting all visible items. Structure the output with these exact three levels:
Level 1 (Categories): Use only these four keys: 'human', 'animal', 'man-made', 'natural'
Level 2 (Item names): Specific names of detected items (e.g., 'person', 'dog', 'car', 'tree')
Level 3 (Attributes): Use ONLY these keys for each item:
  • count: number of instances (integer)
  • location: position in image (use terms like: left/center/right, top/middle/bottom, foreground/background)
  • color: main color(s) if applicable (array of strings)
  • size: relative size (small/medium/large)
  • description: any other relevant details that don't fit above categories (string)
Output valid JSON only. Include only categories that contain detected items. If an attribute doesn't apply to an item (e.g., color for sky), omit that key rather than using null. The 'description' field should capture important characteristics like actions, states, or specific features not covered by other keys.

structured_inventory.prompt_text:
Analyze this image and create a JSON object documenting all visible items. Structure the output with these exact three levels:
Level 1 (Categories): Use only these four keys: 'human', 'animal', 'man-made', 'natural'
Level 2 (Item names): Specific names of detected items (e.g., 'person', 'dog', 'car', 'tree')
Level 3 (Attributes): Use ONLY these keys for each item:
  • count: number of instances (integer)
  • location: position in image (use terms like: left/center/right, top/middle/bottom, foreground/background)
  • color: main color(s) if applicable (array of strings)
  • size: relative size (small/medium/large)
  • description: any other relevant details that don't fit above categories (string)
Output valid JSON only. Include only categories that contain detected items. If an attribute doesn't apply to an item (e.g., color for sky), omit that key rather than using null. The 'description' field should capture important characteristics like actions, states, or specific features not covered by other keys.
